	dprr:hasNoteText "Plut. Sull. 16.8, #. According to Plutarch he received charge of the town of Chaeronea (Plut. Sull. 16.8; 17.6-7; cf. 18.1; and for the praenomen, App. Mith. 66)." ;
	dprr:hasID 4073 .
